Subject: Reminder: Weekly Team Meeting on Wednesday

Dear Team,

I hope this message finds you well. Just a friendly reminder that our weekly team meeting is scheduled for this Wednesday at 10:00 AM.

Please find the Zoom meeting details below:

Meeting Link: [Insert Zoom Meeting Link]
Meeting ID: XXX XXXX XXXX
Passcode: XXXXXX

Agenda:
1. Review of last week's progress

Looking forward to our productive meeting!

Best regards,
